StoreBitFieldInstruction but using base::BitField<FieldType, offset,
bits, ContainerType>::{update,encode} directly (no CodeStubAssembler).

Uses the file-local GetBitFieldSpecialization helper already used by
LoadBitField. When starts_as_zero is set, emits encode(value); otherwise
emits update(container, value) — matching CSA's
UpdateWord*(..., starts_as_zero=true) codepath.
